  "segments": [
    {
      "text": "Mathematically, you should reject the first 37% of people you date.",
      "start": 0.48,
      "end": 3.36,
      "start_ms": 480,
      "end_ms": 3360
    },
    {
      "text": "In computer science, this is called optimal stopping.",
      "start": 4.06,
      "end": 6.08,
      "start_ms": 4060,
      "end_ms": 6080
    },
    {
      "text": "Whether you are hiring an employee, buying a house, or picking a partner, you face a",
      "start": 6.5,
      "end": 9.48,
      "start_ms": 6500,
      "end_ms": 9480
    },
    {
      "text": "paradox.",
      "start": 9.48,
      "end": 9.8,
      "start_ms": 9480,
      "end_ms": 9800
    },
    {
      "text": "If you commit too early, you miss the best option.",
      "start": 10.04,
      "end": 11.74,
      "start_ms": 10040,
      "end_ms": 11740
    },
    {
      "text": "But if you explore for too long, all the good options are gone.",
      "start": 12.02,
      "end": 14.16,
      "start_ms": 12020,
      "end_ms": 14160
    },
    {
      "text": "So mathematicians map the exact probability of winning.",
      "start": 15.04,
      "end": 17.24,
      "start_ms": 15040,
      "end_ms": 17240
    },
    {
      "text": "The answer is exactly 37%.",
      "start": 17.64,
      "end": 19.48,
      "start_ms": 17640,
      "end_ms": 19480
    },
    {
      "text": "For the first 37% of your search, you do not commit to anything.",
      "start": 19.98,
      "end": 22.9,
      "start_ms": 19980,
      "end_ms": 22900
    },
    {
      "text": "You just gather data to figure out what the baseline of good actually looks like.",
      "start": 23.26,
      "end": 26.36,
      "start_ms": 23260,
      "end_ms": 26360
    },
    {
      "text": "Once you pass that 37% mark, the rule changes.",
      "start": 26.78,
      "end": 29.34,
      "start_ms": 26780,
      "end_ms": 29340
    },
    {
      "text": "You immediately lock in the very first option that is better than the best thing you saw",
      "start": 29.86,
      "end": 32.72,
      "start_ms": 29860,
      "end_ms": 32720
    },
    {
      "text": "in your calibration phase.",
      "start": 32.72,
      "end": 33.64,
      "start_ms": 32720,
      "end_ms": 33640
    },
    {
      "text": "You do not wait, you strike.",
      "start": 34.04,
      "end": 35.0,
      "start_ms": 34040,
      "end_ms": 35000
    },
    {
      "text": "It doesn't guarantee a perfect outcome, but it mathematically guarantees the highest",
      "start": 35.74,
      "end": 39.18,
      "start_ms": 35740,
      "end_ms": 39180
    },
    {
      "text": "probability of success.",
      "start": 39.18,
      "end": 40.12,
      "start_ms": 39180,
      "end_ms": 40120
    },
    {
      "text": "So if you're holding out for perfection...",
      "start": 40.84,
      "end": 42.74,
      "start_ms": 40840,
      "end_ms": 42740
    }
  ]
